{"tid":317564,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港其實有二十大","createTime":"2017-07-11T13:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T03:48:10.000Z","uid":123308,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f6b6d248cc291ebc01ac2bacdcac1585b933fd","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"香港其實有二十大（如果計 degree issuing）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fedu-system%2Fpostsecondary%2Flocal-higher-edu%2Finstitutions%2Findex.html&d=%2FhjR98DzZoySTOy%2BaJeKkTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=08d9615f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不過資助得八大 + 公帑資助 HKAPA<br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學 HKUST<br />\n香港大學 HKU<br />\n香港中文大學 CUHK<br />\n香港理工大學 PolyU<br />\n香港教育大學 EdUHK<br />\n嶺南大學 LingU<br />\n香港浸會大學 HKBU<br />\n香港城市大學 CityU<br />\n<br />\n香港演藝學院 HKAPA<br />\n<br />\n香港公開大學 OUHK<br />\n<br />\n香港樹仁大學 SYU<br />\n東華學院 Tung Wah College<br />\n珠海學院 Chu Hai College<br />\n明愛專上學院 Caritas Institute of Higher Education<br />\n香港能仁專上學院 Hong Kong Nang Yan College of Higher Education<br />\n恒生管理學院 HSMC<br />\n明德學院 Centennial College<br />\n宏恩基督教學院 Gratia Christian College<br />\n港專學院 HKCT<br />\n職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹畀大家集思廣益一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話晒以上二十大都係政府認可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8066046351026f9c960f070281880942b7d411f5","tid":317564,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de30f21fdcdb897cdb67148fe7c56622ed8fc0c0","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指大呢</blockquote><br />\n不在教育局二十大名單上"},{"pid":"b77799f4c0c048b3bcdab58bab9053e52f4af7b8","tid":317564,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4acef4ae27fc95b0762a8b4b244e89431b2ea1ff","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>指大呢</blockquote><br />\n不在教育局二十大名單上</blockquote><br />\n咁就知個表唔準la 你都on99</blockquote><br />\n留意呢二十大係自己頒授 degree，不是海外大學中介"},{"pid":"fe6f464355d34851cf43809e44a21e169b1d67a8","tid":317564,"uid":14216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"宏恩基督教學院<br />\n<br />\n呢間咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽都未聽過嘅"},{"pid":"08fe76fc2730be378780efc9ea152af1fe939f06","tid":317564,"uid":93411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宏恩基督教學院<br />\n<br />\n呢間咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽都未聽過嘅</blockquote><br />\nDegree嚟 只是你見識...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5b0721ee44140a07f4ba86d79561210f133462","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宏恩基督教學院<br />\n<br />\n呢間咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽都未聽過嘅</blockquote><br />\n咁即係證明佢宣傳不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eb0c5821710482e69935b21d987694acd2cacb","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會大家都係寧願讀副學位（副學士／高級文憑），都唔會讀 UGC 八大 + HKAPA + OUHK 以外嘅「私立十大」？"},{"pid":"8fc7099fffc36f0e121401ff6b3c27d18015d813","tid":317564,"uid":126029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"公開大學 係咪排第九？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b878aeecbd842b04ca7fd48fdad198a59fdcc8e","tid":317564,"uid":9914,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公開大學 係咪排第九？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得8大架咋  呢d垃圾大學冇資格要頭銜"},{"pid":"f5811a3cb4eba2c1a6c3d8a2e69711812c7f421e","tid":317564,"uid":14216,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宏恩基督教學院<br />\n<br />\n呢間咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽都未聽過嘅</blockquote><br />\nDegree嚟 只是你見識...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 我頭先search咗啦<br />\n<br />\n由恒生管理學院前校長崔康常一手打造的宏恩基督教學院，2015學年首度招收自資學士學位學生，入學人數有51人，但至2016學年，原預計收生學額為180個，但最終只有十分一人、即18人入學。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06049b7a503c1fe8ca864d3759eefcc7d358ac6","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公開大學 係咪排第九？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果講返 UGC 八大前身歷史，本身一成立就已經係大學既大學只有 HKUST，論獲得／有「大學」頭銜既歷史時序：<br />\n- 1912 年：<strong><ins>HKU</ins></strong>: 香港西醫書院 + others -&gt; 香港大學<br />\n- 1963 年：<strong><ins>CUHK</ins></strong>: 成立之初由新亞書院 + 崇基學院 + 聯合書院組成<br />\n- 1991 年：<strong><ins>HKUST</ins></strong> 成立<br />\n- 1994 年：Polytechnic、City Polytechnic、Baptist College 由學院變大學 <strong><ins>PolyU</ins></strong>, <strong><ins>HKBU</ins></strong>, <strong><ins>CityU</ins></strong><br />\n- 1999 年：<strong><ins>LU</ins></strong> 嶺南學院 -&gt; 嶺南大學<br />\n- 2016 年：教育、師範學院合併，HKIEd 教育學院成立（1994 年） -&gt; <strong><ins>EdUHK</ins></strong> 教育大學 (2016年）[/b]<br />\n<br />\nUGC 八大以外：<br />\n- 1996 年：由 1989 年成立嘅香港公開進修學院 Open Learning Institute of Hong Kong 正名為香港公開大學 <strong><ins>OUHK</ins></strong><br />\n- 2007 年：1971 年樹仁書院成立，1976 年變樹仁學院，2006 正名為香港樹仁大學 <strong><ins>SYU</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n論順序嘅時序嚟講，OUHK 係香港第七間命名為「大學」嘅機構，為政府創立，財政獨立，有參加大學聯招 JUPAS，但並不是 UGC 八大"},{"pid":"0819ca1f4a91c0512c9fc9443aee3415fd54c12d","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"今日唔知大家會否考慮到十大私立報名呢？"},{"pid":"c819718f48c32786d73498a25a2cbd6d7a749486","tid":317564,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾先讀自資"},{"pid":"c8c325ac384357da40d1479a22fe7d3b348962b9","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾先讀自資</blockquote><br />\n係香港先會有咁嘅諗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上四年前，四年後，相信會有進步嘅"},{"pid":"0ef081c9202566794997751c92d99c6862eaa3eb","tid":317564,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"能大"},{"pid":"bf75038624fb8d15c39c204a758b58872f2c5787","tid":317564,"uid":11154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>能大</blockquote><br />\n唷"},{"pid":"2d05aa0fe70e357a4b362e9ad4bba39cde477a16","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"其實有副學士，又有私立大學，但私立大學看似處於劣勢，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"04803672a437644b5e3770920a806eb503788b71","tid":317564,"uid":28918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>能大</blockquote><br />\n唷</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49174a51ecae35bf069c6e172ee4f13490ddb4b","tid":317564,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi<br />\n<br />\n佢唔可以做大學 因職業訓練為主"},{"pid":"4ba58c89868bdf4b600b94ce8dc7e282a23a1667","tid":317564,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾先讀自資</blockquote><br />\n係香港先會有咁嘅諗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上四年前，四年後，相信會有進步嘅</blockquote><br />\n係香港嘅自資先咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6dcc66f4fbf3ea50ef3b759517e0ce7ff6629f","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾先讀自資</blockquote><br />\n係香港先會有咁嘅諗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上四年前，四年後，相信會有進步嘅</blockquote><br />\n係香港嘅自資先咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩因素令你覺得香港既私立大學相比海外私立大學係垃圾？"},{"pid":"640b9582e480747cfdd2583c9e287d02153cfc18","tid":317564,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi<br />\n<br />\n佢唔可以做大學 因職業訓練為主</blockquote><br />\n乜原來有職業訓練就不能做大學的講法？"},{"pid":"643bc924a6ca7d02dd9c1b37f0d6bc4079c7e1a4","tid":317564,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi<br />\n<br />\n佢唔可以做大學 因職業訓練為主</blockquote><br />\npolyu 最初咪又係香港工業學院， 唔通又唔可以做大學咩。<br />\nTHEi 雖然柒柒地，但有啲科都有政府資助，又有hkie 認可，仲可以用到ive 啲resources, 私校理工科黎講算咁"}]}